---
title: Hawaiian Prime Rib Burger with Grilled Pineapple and Sweet Mayo
description: There's nothing better than a juicy burger topped with fresh grilled pineapple and sweet mayo, all sandwiched in a soft brioche bun! Who needs take out when you can grill up a restaurant-worthy burger at home?!
